28// Struct that we pass to the decoder per frame to decode. We receive it again
29// in the decoder callback.
30struct RTCH265FrameDecodeParams {
31 RTCH265FrameDecodeParams(RTCVideoDecoderCallback cb, int64_t ts)
32 : callback(cb), timestamp(ts) {}
33 RTCVideoDecoderCallback callback;
34 int64_t timestamp;
35};
36
37@interface RTCVideoDecoderH265 ()
38- (void)setError:(OSStatus)error;
39@end
40
41// This is the callback function that VideoToolbox calls when decode is
42// complete.
43void h265DecompressionOutputCallback(void* decoderRef,
44 void* params,
45 OSStatus status,
46 VTDecodeInfoFlags infoFlags,
47 CVImageBufferRef imageBuffer,
48 CMTime timestamp,
49 CMTime duration) {
50 if (status != noErr || !imageBuffer) {
51 RTCVideoDecoderH265 *decoder = (__bridge RTCVideoDecoderH265 *)decoderRef;
52 [decoder setError:status != noErr ? status : 1];
53 RTC_LOG(LS_ERROR) << "Failed to decode frame. Status: " << status;
54 return;
55 }
56
57 std::unique_ptr<RTCH265FrameDecodeParams> decodeParams(reinterpret_cast<RTCH265FrameDecodeParams*>(params));
58 // TODO(tkchin): Handle CVO properly.
59 RTCCVPixelBuffer* frameBuffer =
60 [[RTCCVPixelBuffer alloc] initWithPixelBuffer:imageBuffer];
61 RTCVideoFrame* decodedFrame = [[RTCVideoFrame alloc]
62 initWithBuffer:frameBuffer
63 rotation:RTCVideoRotation_0
64 timeStampNs:CMTimeGetSeconds(timestamp) * rtc::kNumNanosecsPerSec];
65 decodedFrame.timeStamp = decodeParams->timestamp;
66 decodeParams->callback(decodedFrame);
67}
68
69// Decoder.
70@implementation RTCVideoDecoderH265 {
71 CMVideoFormatDescriptionRef _videoFormat;
72 VTDecompressionSessionRef _decompressionSession;
73 RTCVideoDecoderCallback _callback;
74 OSStatus _error;
75}
76
77- (instancetype)init {
78 if (self = [super init]) {
79 }
80
81 return self;
82}
83
84- (void)dealloc {
85 [self destroyDecompressionSession];
86 [self setVideoFormat:nullptr];
87}
88
89- (NSInteger)startDecodeWithNumberOfCores:(int)numberOfCores {
90 return WEBRTC_VIDEO_CODEC_OK;
91}
92
93- (NSInteger)decode:(RTCEncodedImage*)inputImage
94 missingFrames:(BOOL)missingFrames
95 codecSpecificInfo:(__nullable id<RTCCodecSpecificInfo>)info
96 renderTimeMs:(int64_t)renderTimeMs {
97 RTC_DCHECK(inputImage.buffer);
98 return [self decodeData: (uint8_t *)inputImage.buffer.bytes size: inputImage.buffer.length timeStamp: inputImage.timeStamp];
99}
100
101- (NSInteger)decodeData:(const uint8_t *)data size:(size_t)size timeStamp:(uint32_t)timeStamp {
102 if (_error != noErr) {
103 RTC_LOG(LS_WARNING) << "Last frame decode failed.";
104 _error = noErr;
105 return WEBRTC_VIDEO_CODEC_ERROR;
106 }
107
108 rtc::ScopedCFTypeRef<CMVideoFormatDescriptionRef> inputFormat =
109 rtc::ScopedCF(webrtc::CreateH265VideoFormatDescription(
110 (uint8_t*)data, size));
111 if (inputFormat) {
112 CMVideoDimensions dimensions =
113 CMVideoFormatDescriptionGetDimensions(inputFormat.get());
114 RTC_LOG(LS_INFO) << "Resolution: " << dimensions.width << " x "
115 << dimensions.height;
116 // Check if the video format has changed, and reinitialize decoder if
117 // needed.
118 if (!CMFormatDescriptionEqual(inputFormat.get(), _videoFormat)) {
119 [self setVideoFormat:inputFormat.get()];
120 int resetDecompressionSessionError = [self resetDecompressionSession];
121 if (resetDecompressionSessionError != WEBRTC_VIDEO_CODEC_OK) {
122 return resetDecompressionSessionError;
123 }
124 }
125 }
126 if (!_videoFormat) {
127 // We received a frame but we don't have format information so we can't
128 // decode it.
129 // This can happen after backgrounding. We need to wait for the next
130 // sps/pps before we can resume so we request a keyframe by returning an
131 // error.
132 RTC_LOG(LS_WARNING) << "Missing video format. Frame with sps/pps required.";
133 return WEBRTC_VIDEO_CODEC_ERROR;
134 }
135
136 CMSampleBufferRef sampleBuffer = nullptr;
137 if (!webrtc::H265AnnexBBufferToCMSampleBuffer(
138 (uint8_t*)data, size,
139 _videoFormat, &sampleBuffer)) {
140 return WEBRTC_VIDEO_CODEC_ERROR;
141 }
142 RTC_DCHECK(sampleBuffer);
143 VTDecodeFrameFlags decodeFlags =
144 kVTDecodeFrame_EnableAsynchronousDecompression;
145 std::unique_ptr<RTCH265FrameDecodeParams> frameDecodeParams;
146 frameDecodeParams.reset(
147 new RTCH265FrameDecodeParams(_callback, timeStamp));
148 OSStatus status = VTDecompressionSessionDecodeFrame(
149 _decompressionSession, sampleBuffer, decodeFlags,
150 frameDecodeParams.release(), nullptr);
151#if defined(WEBRTC_IOS)
152 // Re-initialize the decoder if we have an invalid session while the app is
153 // active and retry the decode request.
154 if (status == kVTInvalidSessionErr &&
155 [self resetDecompressionSession] == WEBRTC_VIDEO_CODEC_OK) {
156 frameDecodeParams.reset(
157 new RTCH265FrameDecodeParams(_callback, timeStamp));
158 status = VTDecompressionSessionDecodeFrame(
159 _decompressionSession, sampleBuffer, decodeFlags,
160 frameDecodeParams.release(), nullptr);
161 }
162#endif
163 CFRelease(sampleBuffer);
164 if (status != noErr) {
165 RTC_LOG(LS_ERROR) << "Failed to decode frame with code: " << status;
166 return WEBRTC_VIDEO_CODEC_ERROR;
167 }
168 return WEBRTC_VIDEO_CODEC_OK;
169}
170
171- (void)setCallback:(RTCVideoDecoderCallback)callback {
172 _callback = callback;
173}
174
175- (void)setError:(OSStatus)error {
176 _error = error;
177}
178
179- (NSInteger)releaseDecoder {
180 // Need to invalidate the session so that callbacks no longer occur and it
181 // is safe to null out the callback.
182 [self destroyDecompressionSession];
183 [self setVideoFormat:nullptr];
184 _callback = nullptr;
185 return WEBRTC_VIDEO_CODEC_OK;
186}
187
188#pragma mark - Private
189
190- (int)resetDecompressionSession {
191 [self destroyDecompressionSession];
192
193 // Need to wait for the first SPS to initialize decoder.
194 if (!_videoFormat) {
195 return WEBRTC_VIDEO_CODEC_OK;
196 }
197
198 // Set keys for OpenGL and IOSurface compatibilty, which makes the encoder
199 // create pixel buffers with GPU backed memory. The intent here is to pass
200 // the pixel buffers directly so we avoid a texture upload later during
201 // rendering. This currently is moot because we are converting back to an
202 // I420 frame after decode, but eventually we will be able to plumb
203 // CVPixelBuffers directly to the renderer.
204 // TODO(tkchin): Maybe only set OpenGL/IOSurface keys if we know that that
205 // we can pass CVPixelBuffers as native handles in decoder output.
206 static size_t const attributesSize = 3;
207 CFTypeRef keys[attributesSize] = {
208#if defined(WEBRTC_MAC) || defined(WEBRTC_MAC_CATALYST)
209 kCVPixelBufferOpenGLCompatibilityKey,
210#elif defined(WEBRTC_IOS)
211 kCVPixelBufferOpenGLESCompatibilityKey,
212#endif
213 kCVPixelBufferIOSurfacePropertiesKey,
214 kCVPixelBufferPixelFormatTypeKey
215 };
216 CFDictionaryRef ioSurfaceValue = CreateCFTypeDictionary(nullptr, nullptr, 0);
217 int64_t nv12type = kCVPixelFormatType_420YpCbCr8BiPlanarFullRange;
218 CFNumberRef pixelFormat =
219 CFNumberCreate(nullptr, kCFNumberLongType, &nv12type);
220 CFTypeRef values[attributesSize] = {kCFBooleanTrue, ioSurfaceValue,
221 pixelFormat};
222 CFDictionaryRef attributes =
223 CreateCFTypeDictionary(keys, values, attributesSize);
224 if (ioSurfaceValue) {
225 CFRelease(ioSurfaceValue);
226 ioSurfaceValue = nullptr;
227 }
228 if (pixelFormat) {
229 CFRelease(pixelFormat);
230 pixelFormat = nullptr;
231 }
232 VTDecompressionOutputCallbackRecord record = {
233 h265DecompressionOutputCallback,
234 nullptr,
235 };
236 OSStatus status =
237 VTDecompressionSessionCreate(nullptr, _videoFormat, nullptr, attributes,
238 &record, &_decompressionSession);
239 CFRelease(attributes);
240 if (status != noErr) {
241 [self destroyDecompressionSession];
242 return WEBRTC_VIDEO_CODEC_ERROR;
243 }
244 [self configureDecompressionSession];
245
246 return WEBRTC_VIDEO_CODEC_OK;
247}
248
249- (void)configureDecompressionSession {
250 RTC_DCHECK(_decompressionSession);
251#if defined(WEBRTC_IOS)
252 VTSessionSetProperty(_decompressionSession, kVTDecompressionPropertyKey_RealTime, kCFBooleanTrue);
253#endif
254}
255
256- (void)destroyDecompressionSession {
257 if (_decompressionSession) {
258#if defined(WEBRTC_IOS)
259 VTDecompressionSessionWaitForAsynchronousFrames(_decompressionSession);
260#endif
261 VTDecompressionSessionInvalidate(_decompressionSession);
262 CFRelease(_decompressionSession);
263 _decompressionSession = nullptr;
264 }
265}
266
267- (void)setVideoFormat:(CMVideoFormatDescriptionRef)videoFormat {
268 if (_videoFormat == videoFormat) {
269 return;
270 }
271 if (_videoFormat) {
272 CFRelease(_videoFormat);
273 }
274 _videoFormat = videoFormat;
275 if (_videoFormat) {
276 CFRetain(_videoFormat);
277 }
278}
279
280- (NSString*)implementationName {
281 return @"VideoToolbox";
282}
